    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Process Batch Item\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/jobs — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Respect Rate Limits · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API",
